Package: dicomifier-cli
Architecture: all
Depends: python3-dicomifier (>= ${source:Version}),
         ${python3:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Provides: dicomifier
Conflicts: dicomifier
Replaces: dicomifier
Description: Convert data to and from DICOM (command line tools)
 Dicomifier is a set of tools to convert Bruker to DICOM and DICOM to NIfTI. A
 set of mapping rules is provided, allowing the conservation of meta-data upon
 conversion.
 .
 This package contains the command-line tools.
